highlights.text: Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs Netherlands. “Manchild” is the highest at #12.
“Another Love” by Tom Odell has been on Top Songs Netherlands the longest, at 244 weeks straight.
“Tears” by Sabrina Carpenter is the highest new entry on Top Songs Netherlands at #13.
“Losing Control” by KI/KI and Marlon Hoffstadt is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Netherlands, up 47 spots at #122.
